<bibRefCitation id="A531ABB5D82E855EAA9AC62E0AC7ED5E" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4437.1.1" author="Bogusch, P" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" pagination="1 - 60" refId="B8" refString="Bogusch, P, Hadrava, J, 2018. The bees of the genera Epeolus Latreille, 1802 and Triepeolus Robertson, 1901 (Hymenoptera: Apidae: Nomadinae: Epeolini) of Europe: taxonomy, identification key, distribution, and ecology. Zootaxa 4437 (1): 1 - 60, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4437.1.1" title="The bees of the genera Epeolus Latreille, 1802 and Triepeolus Robertson, 1901 (Hymenoptera: Apidae: Nomadinae: Epeolini) of Europe: taxonomy, identification key, distribution, and ecology." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4437.1.1" volume="4437" year="2018">Bogusch and Hadrava 2018</bibRefCitation>
